                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>A creature bitten by a sinspawn must attempt a @Check[will|dc:28] save as it is assailed by sinful thoughts. The sinswarm can't inflict the same sin effect on multiple targets in the same round until it has inflicted all seven sins at least once.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature is sickened 2 and takes one of the following additional effects, chosen by the GM:</p><ul><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 2} for 1 minute (envy)</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Drained]{Drained 1} (gluttony)</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 2} for 1 minute (greed)</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Stupefied]{Stupefied 2} for 1 minute (lust)</p></li><li><p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Clumsy]{Clumsy 1} and @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.Enfeebled]{Enfeebled 1} for 1 minute (pride)</p></li><li><p>â€“10-foot status penalty to all Speeds for 1 minute (sloth) @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.bestiary-effects.Item.Effect: Sinful Bite]</p></li><li><p>drained 1 and enfeebled 1 for 1 minute (wrath)</p></li></ul>"
                },
